title: 820-3536 water damage no pp5v_s4..
message:
You already said the nboard doesn't even start; why then spending time posting (missing) S3/0 voltages?

If you post PPBUS_G3H and 3V42_G3H measured in various points, also useless; one point is good enough.

Power on sequence I meant signals, not voltages.
Post PM_BATLOW_L, PM_DSW_PWRGD, PM_RSMRST_L, PM_PWRBTN_L.
Trigger SMC_ONOFF_L and check for drop pulse at PM_PWRBTN_L.
If yes, check for pulse at each PM_SLP_Sx_L signal at same time.
